{
  "texts": [
    "Although we mitigated this issue by calibrating the motion tracking sensors for each session and recalibrating them upon detection of discrepancies between participants' actual movements and the corresponding joint data, the inherent nature of the IMU sensor inevitably introduces some drift-related error.",
    "Further, the Cognionics AIM sensor generated spike values during the stroke, and we therefore wrote preprocessing code to process the spike values.",
    "The preprocessing code has been uploaded to the GitHub page.",
    "There was also an interruption in the streaming of data from the gForce EMG armband during the data collection process.",
    "To address this issue, the badminton stroke was stopped and the stream was reconnected to resume data collection."
  ]
}